        <p>Vestre Kirkegård is the largest cemetery in Denmark,
and home to a wide variety of burial sites. You will find Catholic, 
Muslim, Jewish, Faeroese, Greenlandic and several other areas here. </p>
  
    
        <p>This light installation represents the setting sun, a metaphor for death, or the rising sun and new beginnings.
Those Guys Lighting are a group of young light designers
 and engineers from Riga, Latvia, who previously participated in 
Copenhagen Light Festival in 2022 with their interactive installation “On the Wave of Light” along Sydbanestien in Sydhavnen.</p>
   
